column2: SELECT p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, s.z AS RedShift, p.petroMag_u-extinction_u AS mag_u, p.petroMag_g-extinction_g AS mag_g, p.petroMag_r-extinction_r AS mag_r, p.petroMag_i-extinction_i AS mag_i, p.cmodelMag_z-extinction_z AS mag_z, p.deVRad_r FROM galaxy AS p, dbo.fgetNearByObjEq (#, #, #) AS n, galSpecInfo AS s WHERE p.objid = n.objid AND p.specObjID = s.specObjID AND p.specObjID< ># AND s.z BETWEEN # AND # ORDER BY s.z
